message:
I say to God my Rock, “Why have you forgotten me? Why must I go about mourning, oppressed by the enemy?” My bones suffer mortal agony as my foes taunt me, saying to me all day long, “Where is your God?” Why, my soul, are you downcast? Why so disturbed within me? Put your hope in God, for I will yet praise him, my Savior and my God.
Psalm 42:9-11 Heavenly Father we come to you today & we thank you for this new day you have giving us for just letting us open our eyes once more Lord I pray that even in the storm we know that you never forsake us but that a storm is what shapes us & show us that we truly need you Lord so I pray Lord that we force on you & put you first before anything I thank you Lord and I pray this in your mighty heavenly name Amen 🙏🏼🌄🧗‍♀️✝️
Yo just know that even through everything I’m always here I thank you dearly brother

Yeah you always tell me that man next year is your year I know. But word doe your truly a brother to me & there’s never a day I when I don’t have that thought like wow. This is truly my friend even how far or long we can be apart nothing ever change. I say to you scott I thank you for being the loving caring brother you are today I just thank God for the person you are.
Well we our all God’s children and he calls upon all of us on his time but yeah I didn’t you see them doe

Damm yo this message truly made me happy just to know that your truly okay & that your doing well. & what can I say truly God’s been working in me I been submitted myself more & more everyday & just been a blessing with this walk I’m on. But I truly missed you brother & I just thank you for this text you have sent to let me know that your doing amazing.

Hey scott it’s been I min since I seen you & I just hope that your truly doing good & that God truly working in you. I miss you truly homie and just know as far as we can be I’ll always have that love for you & 💭 thoughts of you for you are truly & brother to me. I miss you truly brother & hope your doing amazing through everything much love to you homie hope to see soon 🧗‍♀️🌄

And this is the testimony: God has given us eternal life, and this life is in his Son. Whoever has the Son has life; whoever does not have the Son of God does not have life.
1 John 5:11-12 Heavenly Father I thank you for this new day you have giving us & I pray that we give thanks too you & we all the many works you have done in our lives & our continue doing as we walk with you Lord I pray that we don’t lose site of you when time get hard but glorify you more & know that without suffering we’re truly not walking so I thank you Lord and I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

Therefore, since we have these promises, dear friends, let us purify ourselves from everything that contaminates body and spirit, perfecting holiness out of reverence for God.
2 Corinthians 7:1 Heavenly Father we come to you today & I just thank you for this new day that you have giving us & pray that we don't just give half our life to you but we drop everything that's in the world & what we desired in our eyes & give it all to you at this moment now Lord I thank you Lord and I pray this in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

If we live, we live for the Lord; and if we die, we die for the Lord. So, whether we live or die, we belong to the Lord. For this very reason, Christ died and returned to life so that he might be the Lord of both the dead and the living.
Romans 14:8-9 Heavenly Father I thank you for this new day you have set for us & pray that we know that your blessings is all we need in this world & nothing more but you Lord . & that death or fear go away once we're in your hands so I thank you God for this new day & I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

14 “To the angel of the church in Laodicea write: These are the words of the Amen, the faithful and true witness, the ruler of God’s creation. 15 I know your deeds, that you are neither cold nor hot. I wish you were either one or the other! 16 So, because you are lukewarm—neither hot nor cold—I am about to spit you out of my mouth. 17 You say, ‘I am rich; I have acquired wealth and do not need a thing.’ But you do not realize that you are wretched, pitiful, poor, blind and naked. 18 I counsel you to buy from me gold refined in the fire, so you can become rich; and white clothes to wear, so you can cover your shameful nakedness; and salve to put on your eyes, so you can see.
Revelation 3:14-18 Heavenly Father I thank you for this new day & you said it all in this versus. So I pray that you just keep our thoughts & hearts on you Lord I thank you & pray this all in your name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

For it is by grace you have been saved, through faith —and this is not from yourselves, it is the gift of God— not by works, so that no one can boast. For we are God’s handiwork, created in Christ Jesus to do good works, which God prepared in advance for us to do.
Ephesians 2:8-10 Heavenly Father we come to you today & we thank you for this new awaking you have giving us today. & I pray that we just get right to you & only you Lord not put our  interest that the world or the people of this world need to offer but on what you have giving us & what we need to give back to you our Lord I just thank you for guiding us each day as we live & showing me that without you I would trip  & fall and would just stay with my face plenty to the ground being blinded by this world. I thank you Lord and I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼😂✝️🧗‍♀️

Do you not know that your bodies are temples of the Holy Spirit, who is in you, whom you have received from God? You are not your own; you were bought at a price. Therefore honor God with your bodies.
1 Corinthians 6:19-20 Heavenly Father Lord thank you for giving us this new day to wake upon. To know that we’re in your hands even when hard time come. Lord I thank for giving your beloved son to save all of us from falling in death. Lord I pray that you renew our eyes today & let us only see you Lord keep us fixated on you & only you. & I pray that we know that our body is a holy temple & to recognize that at all times & not to fill it with this world but with you our Lord. I thank you Lord & I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

“And let the peace of God rule in your hearts, to the which also ye are called in one body; and be ye thankful. Let the word of Christ dwell in you richly in all wisdom; teaching and admonishing one another in psalms and hymns and spiritual songs, singing with grace in your hearts to the Lord.”
‭‭Colossians‬ ‭3:15-16‬ ‭Heavenly Father I thank you for this day not for only showing me a new day. But for giving the first thought of you in the morning. To know that through you there is freedom within & out. & praising you is not just a daily thing to check of my to do list. But to show that we truly want to live for you Lord. So I pray that you guide us through this new day & let us not seek the worldly things we adore more but to set aside everything for you our Lord. We thank you Lord & pray this in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

4 “I tell you, my friends, do not be afraid of those who kill the body and after that can do no more. 5 But I will show you whom you should fear: Fear him who, after your body has been killed, has authority to throw you into hell. Yes, I tell you, fear him. 6 Are not five sparrows sold for two pennies? Yet not one of them is forgotten by God. 7 Indeed, the very hairs of your head are all numbered. Don’t be afraid; you are worth more than many sparrows.
Luke 12:4-7 - Heavenly Father we come to you today thanking you praising. Praising you & I just pray that we truly see how gracious you are to us. & with out you there’s true life within & out so I pray that you guide us. To recognize you more & more I thank you Lord & I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

“When tempted, no one should say, “God is tempting me.” For God cannot be tempted by evil, nor does he tempt anyone; but each person is tempted when they are dragged away by their own evil desire and enticed. Then, after desire has conceived, it gives birth to sin; and sin, when it is full-grown, gives birth to death. Don’t be deceived, my dear brothers and sisters. Every good and perfect gift is from above, coming down from the Father of the heavenly lights, who does not change like shifting shadows. He chose to give us birth through the word of truth, that we might be a kind of firstfruits of all he created.”
‭‭James‬ ‭1:13-18‬ - Heavenly Father as we wake up let us be drawn to you more our God. Let us not seek for the eyes of others but force’s on the eyes of you Lord. Keep us firm in your blessing & prayer & word. Let the spirit take full control of the wheel & let the spirit be in slaved. Help us Lord to lean to your understanding more & more I thank you Lord & I pray this all in your mighty heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼🌄✝️🧗‍♀️

May my cry come before you, Lord; give me understanding according to your word. May my supplication come before you; deliver me according to your promise. May my lips overflow with praise, for you teach me your decrees. May my tongue sing of your word, for all your commands are righteous. May your hand be ready to help me, for I have chosen your precepts. I long for your salvation,  Lord, and your law gives me delight. Let me live that I may praise you, and may your laws sustain me. I have strayed like a lost sheep. Seek your servant, for I have not forgotten your commands.
Psalm 119:169-176 - I thank you Lord for this new day & ask that you bless us as we wake & put in our mind & hearts to come to your before everything to praise you truly with no holding back but giving our all complete forces on you & only you Lord let all the things of this world be unnoticed & you be more clear to us. I pray that you show us how meaninglessness everything is with out you Lord but with you Lord you put purpose in this world for us to chase more then just a dream but you Lord I thank you & I Praise you forever & ever in Jesus name we Pray AMEN 🙏🏼✝️🌄🧗‍♀️Goodmorning

Turn my heart toward your statutes and not toward selfish gain. Turn my eyes away from worthless things; preserve my life according to your word. Fulfill your promise to your servant, so that you may be feared. Take away the disgrace I dread, for your laws are good. How I long for your precepts! In your righteousness preserve my life.
Psalm 119:36-40 - Heavenly Father as we come to you today let us not Focus what’s in the world more then you but let’s us know that you are truly more important & that you come before anything in this world let us long for you with all our heart & let the spirit take the way so ask Lord that you guide us through this beautiful morning you have gifted us with. Goodmorning Lord & I thank you for this day you have giving us I pray this all in your heavenly name AMEN 🙏🏼✝️🌄🧗‍♀️

“This is what the Lord says, he who made the earth, the Lord who formed it and established it—the Lord is his name: ‘Call to me and I will answer you and tell you great and unsearchable things you do not know.’
Jeremiah 33:2-3 as we wake let us trusting the Lord more then ourself for we are the foolish one & God is are guider protector our God our Father so don’t look to the world to seek God knowledge for you won’t find nothing but just the worldly knowledge seek within & through prayer as well as our Lord word,stay true to him for God never forsake you Goodmorning & many blessings🙏🏼✝️🌄🧗‍♀️

If any of you lack wisdom, let him ask of God, that giveth to all men liberally, and upbraideth not; and it shall be given him. But let him ask in faith, nothing wavering. For he that wavereth is like a wave of the sea driven with the wind and tossed. Blessed is the man that endureth temptation: for when he is tried, he shall receive the crown of life, which the Lord hath promised to them that love him. Then when lust hath conceived, it bringeth forth sin: and sin, when it is finished, bringeth forth death. For if any be a hearer of the word, and not a doer, he is like unto a man beholding his natural face in a glass:
